        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Same Day Registration Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires states with a voter registration requirement to make same-day voter registration available at the polling place on any day voting is permitted.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
